metadata.name: Icaro #1
metadata.description:
The unique geometric textiles of the Shipibo-Conibo people function as musical scores, woven into imagery.

Video by TAS Visuals, 1440x1440px 41s
Music by Maneesh de Moor
#1 from the Icaro Collection

All proceeds from the sales of this collection will be donated to two non-profit organizations which directly support these indigenous Amazonian tribes.
